models.name: Model 3
models.description: Tesla All-Wheel Drive has two independent motors for improved redundancy, each with only one moving part for minimal maintenance and maximum durability. Unlike traditional all-wheel drive systems, they digitally control torque to the front and rear wheels for far better handling and traction control.

models.name: Model Y
models.description: With the most storage space and towing capacity of any electric SUV, and seating for up to seven adults, Model X delivers maximum utility. Front doors open and close automatically, Falcon Wing doors allow for easier loading and a standard trailer hitch lets you bring your gear anywhere you go.
